OL,3,CPlans for airport conference centre,
OL,4,Chotel and spa refused
OL,6,FMajor plans for a six-storey
OL,7,Fconference centre, restaurant and spa
OL,8,Fopposite Jersey Airport have been
OL,9,Frejected.
OL,11,FThe proposals - which also include a
OL,12,Fluxury hotel with up to 179 rooms and
OL,13,Fa swimming pool - were submitted back
OL,14,Fin August and received strong support
OL,15,Ffrom the business and sports community.
