OL,3,CPlans for airport conference centre,
OL,4,Chotel and spa refused
OL,6,FHowever, despite acknowledging the
OL,7,Fpotential economic benefits, a
OL,8,Fplanning officer's report stated that
OL,9,Fit should be refused due to several
OL,10,Fissues, including how it would be
OL,11,F"overly dominant" and harm the
OL,12,Flandscape.
OL,14,FAt a meeting on Thursday 6 November,
OL,15,FJersey's Planning Committee followed
OL,16,Fthrough on that recommendation to
OL,17,Freject the proposals by four votes to
OL,18,Fthree.
