OL,3,CPlans for airport conference centre,
OL,4,Chotel and spa refused
OL,6,FThey agreed with concerns that the
OL,7,Fsuggested complex would be too large
OL,8,Fand imposing, while it also goes
OL,9,Fagainst the Island Plan.
OL,11,FThis decision has been met with anger
OL,12,Ffrom some, with fresh calls to update
OL,13,Fthe current development framework.
OL,15,FThe President of the island's Chamber
OL,16,Fof Commerce, Lee Madden, says: "We're
OL,17,Foperating on a Bridging Island Plan
OL,18,Fthat's not fit for purpose.
