OL,3,CPlans for airport conference centre,
OL,4,Chotel and spa refused
OL,6,F"If you liken the Island Plan to a
OL,7,FFerrari in an F1 race, it was designed
OL,8,Fsix to seven years ago and we're still
OL,9,Fracing the car; that car wouldn't be
OL,10,Fon the track, it would be in a museum.
OL,11,FIt's absolutely ridiculous."
OL,13,FDavid Kennedy, Chief Executive Officer
OL,14,Fof Jersey Sport, which supports the
OL,15,Fplans, adds: "It's a blow for the
OL,16,Fsports community and tourism.
OL,18,F"We know that sport brings so many
OL,19,Fpeople here every weekend from January
OL,20,Fto December and this was an
OL,21,Fopportunity that's really been missed."
