OL,3,CPlans for airport conference centre,
OL,4,Chotel and spa refused
OL,6,FSt Peter resident, Rowland Huelin,
OL,7,Fsays: "Jersey is closed for business
OL,8,Fat the moment, it's very sad ... we
OL,9,Fshould grab these opportunities for
OL,10,Finvestment to try and prop up our
OL,11,Failing economy and bring some hope to
OL,12,Fthe future of this island.
OL,14,F"The process is broken, fix it."
OL,16,FITV News understands that the
OL,17,Fapplicants, Strive Jersey, intend to
OL,18,Fappeal the decision and ITV News has
OL,19,Falso reached out to those who support
OL,20,Fthe planning decision for comment.
